xpavm is a pulseaudio volume manager for X.
For more information about it's usage check `man xpavm`.

This program requires libxcb and libxcb-image, libxcb-keysyms, libxcb-xkb,
libxcb-shm, libpulse, libfcft and libpixman-1 to be installed.
In order to build this program you need to run `make`.

